OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781709075
OL,3,CFamily friend thought stabbed nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old was 'messing around', trial
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA family friend had thought a nine-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl was "messing around"
OL,9,Fwhen he first saw her lying on the
OL,10,Ffloor ` not realising she had been
OL,11,Ffatally stabbed, a court heard.
OL,13,FOllie Sheppard described seeing Aria
OL,14,FThorpe lying face down in the lounge
OL,15,Fof her home and thought she was
OL,16,Fplaying so called out her name.
OL,18,FHe told Bristol Crown Court that it
OL,19,Fwas only when he saw blood on her arm
OL,20,Fthat he knew it was more serious.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
