OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781709075
OL,3,CFamily friend thought stabbed nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old was 'messing around', trial
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA post-mortem examination found Aria
OL,8,Fhad suffered a single stab wound to
OL,9,Fthe chest and would have "died very
OL,10,Fswiftly from her injury".
OL,12,FThe teenager denies charges of murder
OL,13,Fand manslaughter.
OL,15,FThe trial before Mrs Justice O'Farrell
OL,16,Fcontinues.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
